Name: Parameter
Description: The Parameter class provides information about a specified data parameter.

Name: name
Description: The name attribute provides a word or combination of words by which the object is known.

Name: description
Description: The description attribute provides a statement, picture in words, or account that describes or is otherwise relevant to the object.

Name: value
Description: The value attribute provides a single, allowed numerical or character string value.

Name: MAVEN
Description: The MAVEN class is the container for MAVEN mission-specific metadata elements.

Name: mission_phase_name
Description: The mission_phase_name attribute provides the mission-defined name of a mission phase.

Name: Launch
Description: The period of observations near the time of launch.

Name: Cruise
Description: The period of observations while traveling to a destination.

Name: Orbital Insertion
Description: The period of observations during the orbital insertion.

Name: Prime Mission
Description: The period of observations during the primary objective of the mission.

Name: spacecraft_clock_start_count
Description: The spacecraft_clock_start_count attribute provides the value of the spacecraft clock at the beginning of a time period of interest.

Name: spacecraft_clock_stop_count
Description: The spacecraft_clock_stop_count attribute provides the value of the spacecraft clock at the end of a time period of interest.

Name: mission_event_time_start_count
Description: The mission_event_time_start_count attribute provides the mission event time value at the beginning of a time period of interest.

Name: mission_event_time_stop_count
Description: The mission_event_time_stop_count attribute provides the mission event time value at the end of a time period of interest.
